body_html: In addition to @yaroslavvb suggesting we need a reproducible test case, please provide details about what platform you are using (operating system, architecture). Also include your TensorFlow version. We ask for this in the issue submission template, because it is really difficult to help without that information. Thanks! You could also try with and without GPU.
